      "content": "Increasingly, \"fake news\" functions as a political dismissal tactic rather than a precise descriptor of falsehoods. While it certainly applies to outright misinformation, the term is frequently deployed by partisans to delegitimize opposing viewpoints regardless of factual accuracy. This weaponization of the phrase allows people to reject unfavorable information without having to critically engage with its substance. Therefore, it operates as a rhetorical shield more often than a factual indicator.",
